claim.claim-text:
A light controlling apparatus (100), comprising:
first and second substrates (110, 150) facing each other;
a first electrode (120) on the first substrate (110);
a second electrode (140) on the second substrate (150); and
a polymer dispersed liquid crystal (PDLC) layer (131) and a guest-host liquid crystal (GHLC) layer (132) between the first electrode (120) and the second electrode (140),
wherein the PDLC layer (131) includes droplets (131b) having first liquid crystals (131c), and the GHLC layer (132) includes second liquid crystals (132a) and dichroic dyes (132b).
